omentum score with Value at 65.91. </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Paramount Group Inc <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NYSE\" data-ticker=\"PGRE\" style=\"display:inline-block\">PGRE</span></strong></h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>On May 20, Evercore ISI Group analyst Steve Sakwa upgraded Paramount Group from In-Line to Outperform and raised the price target from $4.5 to $8. The company's stock gained around 42% over the past month and <a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/quote/PGRE\" target=\"_blank\">has a 52-week high</a> of $6.34.</li>\n<li><strong>RSI Value:</strong> 78</li>\n<li><strong>PGRE Price Action:</strong> Shares of Paramount fell 2.6% to close at $6.09 on Thursday.</li>\n<li></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><div class=\"nativo-placement-in-content-ap\"></div><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">BZ Edge Rankings: Find out where other stocks stand—<a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/premium/ideas/benzinga-edge-2#:~:text=Turn%20Market%20Chaos,when%20markets%20rebound\" target=\"_blank\">explore the full comparison now</a>.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\"><strong>Read This Next: </strong></p><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.benzinga.com/25/05/45667868/top-2-materials-stocks-that-are-ticking-portfolio-bombs\" target=\"_blank\">Top 2 Materials Stocks That Are Ticking Portfolio Bombs</a></strong></li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">Photo via Shutterstock</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div><div><div class=\"bz-campaign bz-campaign-bottom-45693552\" data-nosnippet=\"true\"><div class=\"sc-c014f608-0 kUPEDz skeleton min-h-[inherit] animate-pulse variant\" role=\"status\"><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skeleton-child\"></div><div class=\"skel